FBIS3-8426 "dreeu047_b_94002" FBIS-EEU-94-047 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Mar 1994 BULGARIA Further on Prime Minister Berov's Condition Condition Improves AU1003103194 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network in Bulgarian 1000 GMT 10 Mar 94 AU1003103194 Sofia Khorizont Radio Network Language: Bulgarian Article Type:BFN [Text] In the last announcement of the Governmental Press Center it is pointed out that the condition of Prime Minister Lyuben Berov continues to improve. The patient is in good spirits. He has no complaints and responds well to the medicines. We still have no information about the consultation at the Lozenets Hospital, in which the famous Israeli cardiologist Professor Moris Levi is taking part.
